position，How to create a talent profile for a position。”</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 2rem; margin-block-end: 0px; margin-block-start: var(--wp--style--block-gap); max-width: var(--wp--custom--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">For those who“Complex and high-end”Scene，ChrisOften, specific solutions are not provided，But based on one\'s own experience，Provide different dimensions of deduction from the founder\'s perspective，Provide them with a comprehensive feasibility study for evaluation；For relatively basic issues，He prefers to directly bring the concept and methodology of optimization to entrepreneurs，Help them cultivate a qualifiedHRThe thinking logic and working methods of。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 2rem; margin-block-end: 0px; margin-block-start: var(--wp--style--block-gap); max-width: var(--wp--custom--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">“I think<strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">YUEIt must be a‘Teach people to fish’，Instead of‘Teach people fish’Accelerated entrepreneurship</strong><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">implement。</strong>”Chrisexpress，RedwoodHRThe team can assist the founder in addressing critical milestones in recruitment and organization，But he hopes to help companies gradually establish and attract talent from the initial stage、Ability to retain and cultivate talents。</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4; font-size: 2rem; margin-block-end: 0px; margin-block-start: var(--wp--style--block-gap); max-width: var(--wp--custom--content-size); margin-left: auto !important; margin-right: auto !important;\">“If an entrepreneur is not through learning、ponder 